explanation:
• Parallel routes allow multiple routes to be rendered simultaneously within the same page. Parallel routes aredefined using a feature known as slots.

  • Slots help structure our content in a modular fashion. To define a slot, we use the '@folder-name'naming convention.

  • Each slot is then passed as a prop to its corresponding 'layout.jsx' file.
Routing is the mechanism by which requests are connected to the code that handles them.
